## Limitations
The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or the latest industry developments. The information is primarily derived from educational and industry-specific platforms, which may not reflect the full scope of real-world applications and outcomes. Additionally, the data is limited to the context of ITIL 4 and may not apply universally across all service desk environments.